'''圣司提反堂'''（Saint Stephen's Church）位于[[苏格兰|苏格兰]][[爱丁堡新城|爱丁堡新城]]的圣文森街底部。它建于1827-1828年，由建筑师William Henry Playfair（1789年至1857年）设计。其钟楼高{{convert|162|ft|m}}，在欧洲有最长的钟摆。<ref>Capital Walks in Edinburgh: The New Town. David Dick. Neil Wilson, 1996 ISBN 1897784201</ref>

该堂的第一任牧师是威廉·穆尔，他在该堂开了一所夜校，对文盲进行教育。

该堂信徒已经减少。但多年来曾举办[[爱丁堡国际艺穗节|爱丁堡国际艺穗节]]的许多音乐，舞蹈和戏剧活动。

2014年6月27日，电视游戏制片人和[[Rockstar_North|Rockstar North]]总裁Leslie Benzies宣布达成一项协议，以50万英镑购买这座教堂<ref name="leslie">{{cite web |url=http://www.edinburghnews.scotsman.com/news/rockstar-north-chief-buys-st-stephen-s-church-1-3458879 |title=Rockstar North chief buys St Stephen’s Church |publisher=Edinburgh News |date=27 June 2014 |accessdate=2014-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140630005342/http://www.edinburghnews.scotsman.com/news/rockstar-north-chief-buys-st-stephen-s-church-1-3458879 |archive-date=2014-06-30 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他计划保护这座建筑物<ref>{{cite web |author=Phyllis Stephen |url=http://www.theedinburghreporter.co.uk/2014/06/st-stephens-church-future-now-assured/ |title=St Stephen’s Church – future now assured |publisher=The Edinburgh Reporter |date=2014-06-27 |accessdate=2014-06-27 |archive-date=2017-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170910041419/http://www.theedinburghreporter.co.uk/2014/06/st-stephens-church-future-now-assured/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

